Enum KD_configuration.Group

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<KD_configuration.Group>
    Enclosing class:
    KD_configuration

    public static enum KD_configuration.Group
extends java.lang.Enum<KD_configuration.Group>
    Enum Type that setups the lemmatization approach of the tool (Experimental). It is possible to choose among:
    • ALL - Collapses all the key-phrases into the corresponding lemmas
    • BY_LIST - Collapses all the key-phrases into the corresponding lemmas in alist available as configuration files
    • BY_STEM - Collapses all the key-phrases into the corresponding stems (Coming soon)
    • NONE - No Group.
    Default is NONE
    Author:
    Giovanni Moretti - DH Group FBK.
